Still, many people choose to take the car there. Employers may have great impact-

8
00:00:42,933 --> 00:00:45,733
-To switch to a more sustainable mobility.

9
00:00:45,733 --> 00:00:50,633
They can take measures that facilitate, for example, cycle, walk or go collectively.

10
00:00:50,633 --> 00:00:53,167
