This is to be done by identifying the “intermediate” actors-

14
00:01:03,533 --> 00:01:06,833
-What spreads knowledge and ideas about work commuting.

15
00:01:06,833 --> 00:01:10,867
For example, it can be associations or corporate networks.

16
